comment: R-SLA shows that Sullinger (BOS) cleanly strips the ball from Gobert (UTA).
Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Thomas (BOS) that affects his FOM away from the ball.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Favors (UTA) touched the ball last prior to going OOB was confirmed.
Bradley (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Hayward's (UTA) in the post and he cleanly blocks his turnaround jump shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) grabs Johnson's (BOS) jersey, affecting his position for the rebound. Immediately following the jersey grab, Johnson pulls Gobert's left arm during his effort to retrieve the ball.
Hood (UTA) commits a take foul on Bradley (BOS).
Mack (UTA) commits a take foul on Bradley (BOS).
Favors (UTA) commits a take foul on Johnson (BOS).
Hayward (UTA) extends his arms as he sets the screen on Turner (BOS) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
